Pseudocode for drawing the window below:

+===+===+
|   |   |
|   |   |
|   |   |
+===+===+
|   |   |
|   |   |
|   |   |
+===+===+

Pseudocode:

Create a constant for the SUB_HEIGHT, the height of a single window.

Draw line
Draw window
Draw line
Draw window
Draw line

Draw line
    Draw a '+'
    Draw SUB_HEIGHT number of '='
    Draw a '+'
    Draw SUB_HEIGHT number of '='
    Draw a '+'

Draw window
    Draw the following three times:
        Draw a '|'
        Draw SUB_HEIGHT number of ' '
        Draw a '|'
        Draw SUB_HEIGHT number of ' '
        Draw a '|'
